<div class="music-list" style="margin-top:20px;"><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/nothing-else.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/nothingelese.jpg" alt="Nothing Else / Lorn" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/nothing-else.php">Nothing Else<br />Lorn</a></h4><p>軽快なヒップホップ。エレクトロニカのような雰囲気を合わせ持っていて明るい雰囲気とリラックス効果を同時に楽しむことができるような音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003M3ZR28?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003M3ZR28" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Nothing Else-Lorn']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fnothing-else%252Fid373055420%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Nothing Else-Lorn']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/les-violons-ivres.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/acogara.jpg" alt="Les Violons Ivres / Agoria" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/les-violons-ivres.php">Les Violons Ivres<br />Agoria</a></h4><p>シンプルな音なので会話の邪魔になることはありません。かといって静かすぎるわけでもなく。とてもバランスの取れた食事のための音楽でしょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000PDZIMM?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000PDZIMM" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Les Violons Ivres-Agoria']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fles-violons-ivres-ep%252Fid254089531%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Les Violons Ivres-Agoria']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/2010-1.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/2010studio.jpg" alt="2010 / Studio Apartment" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/2010-1.php">2010<br />Studio Apartment</a></h4><p>少し盛り上げたい方にはこちらがおすすめ。キャッチーなフレーズがたくさん含まれているので食事を楽しみながら気分を持ち上げることができます。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003DTQLMQ?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003DTQLMQ" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', '2010-Studio Apartment']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252F2010%252Fid370349474%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', '2010-Studio Apartment']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/koop-islands.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/koop.jpg" alt="Koop Islands / Koop" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/koop-islands.php">Koop Islands<br />Koop</a></h4><p>ジャズといっても夜が似合うようなものではなく、軽いかんじで聴けるのが本作品。ヴォーカルが入っているので聴きやすく、落ちついてランチが取れるでしょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000VI6T9C?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000VI6T9C" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Koop Islands-Koop']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fkoop-islands%252Fid350318863%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Koop Islands-Koop']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/gilles-peterson-brazilika-mixed-version.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/brazilila.jpg" alt="Gilles Peterson Brazilika (Mixed Version) / Gilles Peterson" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/gilles-peterson-brazilika-mixed-version.php">Gilles Peterson Brazilika (Mixed Version)<br />Gilles Peterson</a></h4><p>ブラジリアンなランチタイムを過ごしたいならこちらがおすすめです。暑苦しいようなタイプの音ではなく、非常にさわやかです。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002AG2NQG?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002AG2NQG" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Gilles Peterson Brazilika (Mixed Version)-Gilles Peterson']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fgilles-peterson-brazilika%252Fid322108040%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Gilles Peterson Brazilika (Mixed Version)-Gilles Peterson']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/amour.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/amore.jpg" alt="Amour / Jimpster" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/amour.php">Amour<br />Jimpster</a></h4><p>大人な雰囲気を持ったヒップホップ。会話も楽しめて雰囲気もある、何重もの効果を持った食事に最適な作品と言えるでしょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000FEBU2S?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000FEBU2S" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Amour-Jimpster']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Famour%252Fid290267486%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Amour-Jimpster']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/balance.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/balance.jpg" alt="Balance / Isoul8" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/balance.php">Balance<br />Isoul8</a></h4><p>とてもシンプルな音の編成。音楽だけ聴くよりもBGMとして聴く方が合っているかもしれません。こちらもおすすめです。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000FEB6DQ?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000FEB6DQ" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Balance-Isoul8']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fbalance%252Fid168493198%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Balance-Isoul8']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/sincerely-hot-1.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/sincerely.jpg" alt="Sincerely Hot / Domenico + 2" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/sincerely-hot-1.php">Sincerely Hot<br />Domenico + 2</a></h4><p>ブラジルのポップ音楽。ラジオから流れてくるようなとても明るい音楽。重い雰囲気は全くないのでゆっくりと聴いて楽しめます。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0002WZT66?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0002WZT66" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Sincerely Hot-Domenico + 2']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fsincerely-hot%252Fid23253366%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Sincerely Hot-Domenico + 2']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/ultraviolet.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/ultraviolet.jpg" alt="Ultraviolet / Kid Sister" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/ultraviolet.php">Ultraviolet<br />Kid Sister</a></h4><p>最後にヒッピホップ作品。細かいアレンジですが、食事の邪魔になるようなことはありません。都会を感じる音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002NPUCLW?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002NPUCLW" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Ultraviolet-Kid Sister']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fultraviolet%252Fid366916905%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Ultraviolet-Kid Sister']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div></div>

